Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}被吞噬的群星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:52.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}虚无缥缈的灰色积雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:57.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}凝视着叹息之窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我从未梦想过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}会前往冻成坚冰的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}去寻找你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:11.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}愿望　飞舞到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:16.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}寂寞的夜空中　破碎了
