Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能进行左手再生治疗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干部的干细胞发现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说可能是因为Gundam的光束兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起细胞障碍导致的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的哦  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要乖乖回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:55.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}美国  联合国会场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于Celestial Being的多次凶恶的恐怖袭击行为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:03:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合  人类革新联盟和AEU缔结了军事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣布  要在联合国的管理下\N为了消灭Celestial Being而采取军事行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三方阵营在联合国的管理下发表了军事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此  将诞生有史以来最大规模的联合国军队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事情正像Celestial Being预想的那样发展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近过激的武力介入  是为了使联合国军队统一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以这么考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使世界团结一致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Celestial Being的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用战争来否定战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了获得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这就是你所希望的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划的第一阶段总算是结束了  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体的行动成了导火索  这是否能改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各国的军事基地因三位一体而受到了重创
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种状况下即使统一军队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也不会有什么结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会招致世人的失望和反感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的信息未明示的三位一体的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于吠陀的数据被窜改这一事实的无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来自皇·李·诺瑞加的密码消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请Meister和机体一起返回普特利麦奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  有作战会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看看联合国军队的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你预测过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  不预先准备一下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  你能否带上拉塞去拿GN ARMS呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN ARMS生产好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之只有一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余下的成员准备进行飞上来的Gundam的回收作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要投入GN ARMS了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况所迫  不得已而为之啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:37.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}联合  美国  伊利诺斯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  是关于从新型Gundam夺来的光刀的调查结果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来Celestial Being内部出现了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说叛徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还送来了与Gundam同型号的发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及搭设了这种发动机的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是30台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才作了那样的发表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供来的机体的机师\N应该会从Over Flags的队员中进行挑选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  队长会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚决反对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用Flag来打倒Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在霍华德·梅森的墓前这么发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过队长  以Flag的性能是抵挡不了Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉大丈夫  一言既出驷马难追
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:43.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人革联  俄罗斯南部  驻军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam的主要机构…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据资料  正式名称好像叫做GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分配给我们人革联的GN Drive有10个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  机师的人选由你来定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来做新型机的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说少尉释放的脑量子波会对长翅膀的机师产生影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个优点  不使用就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样可就不好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}AEU  法国  基地内士官宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师候补的话  集中AEU所属国的王牌就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  是否要加入那个男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大校  是我  帕特里克·克拉萨乌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请大校吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:07:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界现在正要迎来巨大的变革期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此你有考虑过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真是无可救药的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:25.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}线性火车公司  会长别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是JNN吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们说  对此无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人气真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谈这个  机体的运输好像很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借款之事就让我去办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那·哈贝总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就开门见山直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否把运输中的新型机中的1台让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不管是联合还是AEU都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您以总裁的权限让我加入军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隶属外籍战士部队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是加里·比亚吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你很有天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你为何那么想要驾驶那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠了某个人3次人情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这有点关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭我的感觉  我认为在以后的未来  佣兵将变得不再需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少想去一个能够作战的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了  这只是我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能考虑一下  总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那Celestial什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取材空手而归  该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说总裁在面谈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是JNN的特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问两三个问题  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JNN的记者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可以  但我正有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否在车上谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用问了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫绢江·克洛斯罗德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  有你这样的美女记者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要问我的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果搞错了请见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比亚吉先生你之前是否会见了火车公司的总裁拉古那·哈贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从事的是流通行业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了确认物资的流通而会见了总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个特意去见总裁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是私事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  私事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告诉我些关于这些物资的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN…Drive？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是与线性火车公司有关的什么器材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是驱动MS的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧  是Celestial Being拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那个克鲁吉斯的少年兵为机师的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁吉斯的…少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诱拐  洗脑  接受战斗训练  并成为游击兵这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我所为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个战争狂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战争喜欢到了忍受不了的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为人类的本能冲动而生的最恶劣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…又出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那只鬼鬼祟祟的老鼠处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这是个威胁舆论支持的好活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  贪心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙  沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}联合  高轨道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得亚历桑德罗大人您没必要特地和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你辛苦得来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我亲眼看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这是柯纳一族长久以来的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历桑德罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  应该说柯纳一家在好几代之前就策划了对计划的介入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要吠陀还在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个时候  很偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的面前有天使降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你  李本兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我报答您把我捡回来的大恩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到你要查明本体的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了那么长的时间  非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本兹  你真是我的天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}非洲大陆  西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直让我到处工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在突然中止联络  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我啊  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长考虑这些复杂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克哥就是这种类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿我当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个哈罗  欠砍是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔  哈罗是三位一体不可或缺的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大哥  开玩笑的  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那发来了任务计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容跟以前的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战在三天后开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等着这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么通过防卫系统的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  既然你们发现了这里  那就别想轻易离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  迈克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位美女  我记得在吠陀的资料里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被记住是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Celestial Being的特工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我的搭档红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来到这里就知道你们的能力很高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  找我们有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是来打声招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体小队跟我们一样隶属Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为特工的我们支援你们是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是被你们的Gundam攻击了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我也有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不是他们那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是中立派吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我遵从的是伊奥利亚·修亨伯格提出的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等需要的时候就看你的援助了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应不告诉他们  告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么放他们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  能用的牌自然是多多益善了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美女  真是美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别带有偏见  别带有偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好么  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being和他们敌对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为三位一体引发了世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就那么厌恶现在的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我觉得不改变的话  破坏了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  着舰完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止还没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体也没有活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违反命令的惩罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候有这规定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  三位一体开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  他们的攻击目标是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进线路上的军事基地是人革联广州军区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:21.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}人革联  广州方面军驻地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测班呼叫所有人员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判定为新型Gundam的三台MS正从S9788方向飞来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将对本基地进行军事介入…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为之前的事等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好干一场  行么  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战上没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一架来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我中  给我中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕  集中火力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打我后面  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂鱼  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该收场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始对接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Exia吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是10机的编队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  放出GN粒子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是Celestial Being吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶武GN-X部队  开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是虎之子的10台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被打成重伤哦  上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这种机动性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这性能真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  这机体  厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam已经不足为惧了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体可以跟上我的反应速度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢把Fang…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许争论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看下面的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明受到了那么严重的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉你是第一次尝到这种味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体似乎从战斗空域离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革联方面把搭载了太阳炉的MS投入了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳炉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  有情报从吠陀那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就会变成Gundam之间的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样  世界仍在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面到底会有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请  亚历桑德罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  作为Celestial Being基础的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}同じ笑顔してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:25.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}そんな僕らも幾年も重ねすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:28.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}すれ違う景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:34.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}受け入れられずにもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:41.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:46.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:53.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:58.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:18.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:30.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有着相同的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:25.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那样的我们也已过了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:28.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交错的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:34.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}无法接受并急躁着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:41.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}舍弃了无用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:46.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}给予这世界以温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:53.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便显示出勇气　即便逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:58.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一个人亦是无法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心灵深处的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延续...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:18.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由于不可忘记　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要离去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:30.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}还要留在这广阔大地同伴们的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的MS对Gundam发起了攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对追求着根除战争梦想的人们的判罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「毁灭之路」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是世界的回应


